<bibRefCitation author="Dall, W. H." box="[415,541,1744,1770]" pageId="29" pageNumber="496" pagination="1 - 3" refId="ref10618" refString="Dall, W. H. (1878) Descriptions of new forms of mollusks from Alasca contained in the collections of the National Museum. Proceedings of the United States National Museum, 1, 1 - 3. https: // doi. org / 10.5479 / si. 00963801.1" type="journal article" year="1878">Dall, 1878</bibRefCitation>
